widearea_code2cat01_codevarnamlongwide

vars <- vars %>%
  #
  dplyr::mutate(pref_code=substr(x=area_code,start=1,stop=2)) %>%
  #

  #

  #
  dplyr::mutate(varnam=dplyr::case_when(
